Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成为了通称"ASCAN"的宇航员候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:06.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ASCAN："AStronaut CANdidate"的缩写，意思就是"宇航员候补生"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和其他国家的候补生一起进行基础训练
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到了训练举办地 美国休斯敦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤治 芹夏小姐 北村小姐 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JAXA的老妈小町 和宇航员前辈紫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.59,0:00:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还有我..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and 阿波
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练将在十天后开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前大家要先搞定住房问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后等待着我们的到底是什么样的训练呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就是日日人的大哥么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸上透着一股傻气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也没有从军经验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但落后于弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上这副松松散散的蠢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能知道这家伙是个没药救的蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员啊..那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像舞台演员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名为“室长”的舞台监督
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有名为“训练教官”的导演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们又是什么呢？小六
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的咖啡..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜得出奇..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色 紫色 粉红和黄色..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连运动饮料都这么五彩缤纷的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此地 便是美国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但看起来好甜 而且好像有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然要在这里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只好入乡随俗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就买它了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再买瓶红色的给贤治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤治..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的贤治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 阿六..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次在这两年训练之中..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还是不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这样最让人在意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啦 因为就算说了也没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我觉得这事不该现在说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而让人更在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 贤治那家伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底向紫先生问了些什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..“不该现在说”也就意味着..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不该现在问”对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是那种刨根问底的不知趣的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再问贤治了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问问紫先生吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连家具都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里挺不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得这里不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超市也很近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且..厨房好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做好多好多！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独居生活是完全够了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房租是个问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 这里多少钱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多打点折扣啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两位女孩子可是宇航员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啦 便宜一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这..这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是让宇航员住到自家公寓..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让这里的格调提升好几个档次呐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 便宜了便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町女士的英文真流利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像当地人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我以前曾在加利福尼亚住过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得一口加利福尼亚口音的英文哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇上什么麻烦就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会马上赶过来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦..好强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃棉花软糖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿个四个吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 忍者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是不是又手闲了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不会又是油性笔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫先生被称为“忍者”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 小六！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:57.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍忍~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶..这个月第二回了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么净挑我啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飞机上对贤治说的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..到底是哪番话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是..训练中怎样怎样的..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是那个..大概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点后悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这事不该现在说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是贤治他问了我不少问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不小心就说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次候补生的2年训练期间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然训练完毕也不例外..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说一定会出现数名落选者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说他们放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃去宇宙的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人到训练之中才会察觉到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察觉到自己不适合这个事业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎..怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..只要自己不放弃就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在害怕什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那“不适合的几位”之中有我的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千辛万苦走到这一步..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后的最后居然梦想破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样简直就像..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多..多哈的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！别说出下面两个字！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你不用在意啦 小六
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后才是真正累人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杰森·巴特勒室长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶~那就是室长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员啊..那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像舞台演员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名为“室长”的舞台监督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:17.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(500,0)}宇航员室长 舞台监督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有名为“训练教官”的导演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(500,0)}训练教官 导演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们又是什么呢？小六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们这些演员之中的哪一位站上舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就取决于舞台监督的偏好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小宫..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在好几年前就已经称自己为“宇航员”了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到现在依然是上不了舞台的演员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我回去训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会啦 小六
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶..他又来了..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天的咖啡..甜得出奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我自然而然地记住了那个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我决定用租的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三室一厅一厨带车库
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人住的话太大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间也有多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房租当然也会比较贵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我为什么选这么大的房子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是想碰碰运气啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能让那家伙来这边..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不抱希望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 以后再打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦！美智子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮佛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦好痛苦 要死人了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么吗 珍妮佛变得更加圆滚滚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这两人认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 被你看出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在是汉堡包最好吃的季节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了又想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉堡包一整年都很好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务控制中心！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是头一回见到呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕上显示的是现在的月球表面吧？珍妮佛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 弗莱迪和巴迪正在作业中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场直播现场直播！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 珍妮佛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日人的情况看不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日人现在正在就寝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4小时之后才会起床
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 日日人没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明刚刚遇上了那种事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始整天嚷嚷着要进行舱外活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是日日人和达米安还没有得到医生的许可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那两个人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务中应该已经没有舱外活动的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真..真的假的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地内还有螺旋藻的低重力培养实验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及蛋白质结晶化以及分析之类..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他要做的事情还堆积如山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以完全不会无聊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这也没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样反而更让人安心么..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CES-51班组滞留月球表面已经超过2个月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他们每一天..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在刷新着月球表面长期滞留记录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月我们对远在月球的南波日日人宇航员颁发了勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的功绩有两项出色的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一是拯救了负伤的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二是让自己也平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们NASA最大的主题就在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“月面生活的实现和持续”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有“人类抵达火星”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们的梦想永无止尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了这些梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们跟我作出约定 一定要平安回到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是身为室长的我杰森·巴特勒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及这里的30名候补生之间的..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室长的严肃话题到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始聚会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？很严肃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是我们的同期生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨克·麦康纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这人虽然不懂规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还请多多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..我是南波·六太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人和我们同期吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去自我介绍吗？文斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是训练教官..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是训练教官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我介绍这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在所有人面前一次了结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们的名字还..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的脸和名字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经基本掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一个 新田也让她看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她为我们占卜了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然光看外表就知道芹夏小姐是独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而北村小姐是五人姐弟..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我有妻子 孩子和一个妹妹都被她猜中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说还有预知能力哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经算是超能力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..你..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个有家室的姐姐..还有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个弟弟是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个弟弟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实有个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:20:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..我没有弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我猜错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也很厉害了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也来算算我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是来自日本的南波六太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿曼蒂·帕特尔 来自印度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如此！回答正确！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很有名嘛 南波日日人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那么能不能帮我算算其他事情呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如未来的展望之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样呢..好像..感觉很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 阿曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 比起米饭 更喜欢用囊饼来搭配咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个被你发现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我现在才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次我教你做手工的馕饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等等..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才明显露出了很不妙的表情吧..阿曼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿曼蒂的占卜到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一定会有劫难降临到我身上！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要遵守我的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把本来需要花费两年的基础训练
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一年半之内完成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 如果能快点追上日日人的话那倒不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最初的训练是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 宇宙兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中永远放个计步器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后请你们一直走下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的仅此而已
